item.title: Workshop: An Introduction to SAP Predictive Analytics
item.description: Logistics / Setup Date: Thursday April 26, 2018 Time: 2-2:50 pm Location: MLIB 442 Presenter: Dr. Arash Negahban, CSUC College of Business Description Join us for a peek into the predictive analytics arena from a Business perspective – using the SAP software.This is also a great opportunity to learn about the SAP resources we have available on campus. SAP Predictive Analytics is the visualization tool for SAP, the world’s largest business software company founded in 1972 and headquartered in Germany.
